---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="How It Works — authored.systems" description="Watch an operation come to life, one primitive at a time.">
  <div class="explain">
    <!-- Sticky graphic -->
    <div class="graphic">
      <svg id="diagram" viewBox="0 0 800 500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Layout:
             Event(150,100) -> Policy(400,100) -> Procedure(650,100)
                                                       |
             Ledger(150,400) <- Asset(400,400) <- Person(650,400)
             Ledger feeds back to Event (left side, up)
        -->

        <!-- Connecting paths (hidden initially, revealed per-step) -->
        <line id="path-event-policy" x1="200" y1="100" x2="350" y2="100" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="2" opacity="0" />
        <line id="path-policy-procedure" x1="450" y1="100" x2="600" y2="100" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="2" opacity="0" />
        <line id="path-procedure-person" x1="650" y1="150" x2="650" y2="350" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="2" opacity="0" />
        <line id="path-person-asset" x1="600" y1="400" x2="450" y2="400" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="2" opacity="0" />
        <line id="path-asset-ledger" x1="350" y1="400" x2="200" y2="400" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="2" opacity="0" />

        <!-- Chevron arrows on paths -->
        <polygon id="arrow-1" points="345,95 355,100 345,105" fill="#e5e5e3" opacity="0" />
        <polygon id="arrow-2" points="595,95 605,100 595,105" fill="#e5e5e3" opacity="0" />
        <polygon id="arrow-3" points="645,345 650,355 655,345" fill="#e5e5e3" opacity="0" />
        <polygon id="arrow-4" points="455,395 445,400 455,405" fill="#e5e5e3" opacity="0" />
        <polygon id="arrow-5" points="205,395 195,400 205,405" fill="#e5e5e3" opacity="0" />

        <!-- Event node — lightning bolt in circle -->
        <g id="node-event" class="node" opacity="0">
          <circle cx="150" cy="100" r="44" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2" />
          <path d="M148,76 L140,100 L150,98 L144,124 L160,94 L149,96 Z" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          <text x="150" y="158" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#1a1a1a">Event</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Policy node — document with lines -->
        <g id="node-policy" class="node" opacity="0">
          <rect x="358" y="60" width="84" height="80" rx="6" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2" />
          <!-- Dog-ear fold -->
          <path d="M422,60 L422,72 L442,72" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <!-- Rule lines -->
          <line x1="372" y1="84" x2="428" y2="84" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4" />
          <line x1="372" y1="94" x2="420" y2="94" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4" />
          <line x1="372" y1="104" x2="424" y2="104" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4" />
          <line x1="372" y1="114" x2="412" y2="114" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4" />
          <text x="400" y="158" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#1a1a1a">Policy</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Procedure node — checklist with checkboxes -->
        <g id="node-procedure" class="node" opacity="0">
          <rect x="608" y="60" width="84" height="80" rx="6" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2" />
          <!-- Checkbox rows -->
          <rect x="620" y="76" width="10" height="10" rx="2" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <path d="M622,81 L624,84 L629,78" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <line x1="636" y1="82" x2="678" y2="82" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4" />
          <rect x="620" y="94" width="10" height="10" rx="2" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <path d="M622,99 L624,102 L629,96" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <line x1="636" y1="100" x2="678" y2="100" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4" />
          <rect x="620" y="112" width="10" height="10" rx="2" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <line x1="636" y1="118" x2="678" y2="118" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4" />
          <text x="650" y="158" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#1a1a1a">Procedure</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Person node — bust silhouette -->
        <g id="node-person" class="node" opacity="0">
          <circle cx="650" cy="400" r="44" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2" />
          <!-- Head -->
          <circle cx="650" cy="388" r="10" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <!-- Shoulders -->
          <path d="M634,416 Q634,404 650,404 Q666,404 666,416" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <text x="650" y="458" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#1a1a1a">Person</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Extra person nodes for optimization (step 9) — row at y=400 -->
        <g id="node-person-b" class="node" opacity="0">
          <circle cx="540" cy="400" r="30" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <circle cx="540" cy="392" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <path d="M530,412 Q530,404 540,404 Q550,404 550,412" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <text x="540" y="440" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="8" fill="#6b6b6b">4.2 / 8mi</text>
        </g>
        <g id="node-person-c" class="node" opacity="0">
          <circle cx="760" cy="400" r="30" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <circle cx="760" cy="392" r="6" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <path d="M750,412 Q750,404 760,404 Q770,404 770,412" fill="none" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <text x="760" y="440" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="8" fill="#6b6b6b">3.9 / 14mi</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Asset node — rounded box with tag -->
        <g id="node-asset" class="node" opacity="0">
          <rect x="356" y="368" width="88" height="64" rx="12" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2" />
          <!-- ID tag line -->
          <line x1="376" y1="388" x2="424" y2="388" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.4" />
          <!-- Barcode-like hash marks -->
          <line x1="382" y1="400" x2="382" y2="414" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="388" y1="400" x2="388" y2="414" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2.5" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="394" y1="400" x2="394" y2="414" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="399" y1="400" x2="399" y2="414" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="405" y1="400" x2="405" y2="414" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="411" y1="400" x2="411" y2="414" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="417" y1="400" x2="417" y2="414" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2" opacity="0.3" />
          <text x="400" y="458" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#1a1a1a">Asset</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Ledger node — open book / stacked rows -->
        <g id="node-ledger" class="node" opacity="0">
          <rect x="108" y="368" width="84" height="64" rx="4" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="2" />
          <!-- Spine -->
          <line x1="150" y1="368" x2="150" y2="432" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <!-- Left page lines -->
          <line x1="118" y1="382" x2="144" y2="382" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="118" y1="392" x2="144" y2="392" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="118" y1="402" x2="144" y2="402" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="118" y1="412" x2="140" y2="412" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <!-- Right page lines -->
          <line x1="156" y1="382" x2="182" y2="382" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="156" y1="392" x2="182" y2="392" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="156" y1="402" x2="182" y2="402" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="156" y1="412" x2="178" y2="412" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <text x="150" y="458" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="13" font-weight="600" fill="#1a1a1a">Ledger</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Chaos flood (appears at step 7) -->
        <g id="chaos-flood" opacity="0">
          <!-- Blurry overwhelm circle behind Event -->
          <circle cx="150" cy="100" r="70" fill="#cc3333" opacity="0.08" />
          <!-- Squiggle paths at varying angles -->
          <path class="squiggle-animate" d="M 10,100 Q 25,80 35,100 Q 45,120 55,100 Q 65,80 75,100 Q 85,120 95,100" stroke="#cc3333" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <path class="squiggle-animate" d="M 30,50 Q 45,35 55,55 Q 65,75 80,55 Q 95,35 110,55" stroke="#e05533" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <path class="squiggle-animate" d="M 50,150 Q 60,130 75,155 Q 90,175 105,150 Q 115,130 130,150" stroke="#cc3333" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <path class="squiggle-animate" d="M 180,45 Q 200,30 215,50 Q 230,70 245,45" stroke="#e07744" stroke-width="1.8" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round" />
          <!-- Scattered emoji/text fragments -->
          <text class="squiggle-animate" x="20" y="70" font-size="18">📸</text>
          <text class="squiggle-animate" x="210" y="160" font-size="18">🎤</text>
          <text class="squiggle-animate" x="80" y="170" font-size="18">💬</text>
          <text class="squiggle-animate" x="230" y="70" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="14" fill="#cc3333" font-weight="700">???</text>
        </g>

        <!-- AI perception filter bar + glow (step 8) -->
        <g id="ai-filter" opacity="0">
          <rect x="90" y="60" width="20" height="80" rx="4" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.12" />
          <rect x="94" y="65" width="12" height="70" rx="3" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.6" />
          <text x="100" y="52" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" font-weight="600" fill="#2563eb">AI</text>
        </g>

        <!-- AI optimization: underline + BEST MATCH badge (step 9) -->
        <g id="ai-opt-highlight" opacity="0">
          <rect id="ai-sweep-bar" x="530" y="440" width="0" height="3" rx="1.5" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.5" />
          <rect x="620" y="448" width="60" height="16" rx="3" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0" id="ai-best-badge-bg" />
          <text id="ai-best-label" x="650" y="460" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="8" font-weight="700" fill="#fff" opacity="0">BEST MATCH</text>
        </g>

        <!-- AI pattern detection: ledger scan lines (step 10) -->
        <g id="ai-ledger-lines" opacity="0">
          <line x1="120" y1="385" x2="180" y2="385" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="ledger-scan-line" />
          <line x1="125" y1="392" x2="175" y2="392" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="ledger-scan-line" />
          <line x1="122" y1="399" x2="178" y2="399" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="ledger-scan-line" />
          <line x1="128" y1="406" x2="172" y2="406" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="ledger-scan-line" />
          <line x1="124" y1="413" x2="176" y2="413" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0" class="ledger-scan-line" />
        </g>
        <!-- Horizontal dashed line from Ledger to Policy (step 10) -->
        <line id="ai-pattern-line" x1="200" y1="300" x2="370" y2="300" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="6 3" fill="none" opacity="0" />
        <text id="ai-pattern-label" x="285" y="318" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0">pattern → suggest rule update</text>

        <!-- Final state: AI text labels at three edge points (step 11) -->
        <g id="ai-edge-labels" opacity="0">
          <text x="100" y="56" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" font-weight="600" fill="#2563eb">AI</text>
          <text x="650" y="345" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" font-weight="600" fill="#2563eb">AI</text>
          <text x="150" y="340" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" font-weight="600" fill="#2563eb">AI</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Step 0: Blue AI blob — "You've been told AI is the answer" -->
        <g id="ai-blob" opacity="0">
          <circle cx="400" cy="250" r="80" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.15" />
          <circle cx="400" cy="250" r="60" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.25" />
          <circle cx="400" cy="250" r="36" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.4" />
          <text x="400" y="255" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="20" font-weight="700" fill="#fff">AI</text>
          <!-- Messy unlabeled arrows in/out -->
          <line x1="260" y1="180" x2="348" y2="222" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4" />
          <line x1="280" y1="330" x2="352" y2="280" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4" />
          <line x1="520" y1="170" x2="450" y2="220" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4" />
          <line x1="540" y1="310" x2="452" y2="272" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4" />
          <line x1="400" y1="120" x2="400" y2="192" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4" />
          <line x1="400" y1="380" x2="400" y2="308" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1.5" opacity="0.4" />
          <!-- Small labels on arrows -->
          <text x="250" y="175" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="8" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.5">events?</text>
          <text x="265" y="340" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="8" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.5">people?</text>
          <text x="525" y="165" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="8" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.5">data?</text>
          <text x="535" y="322" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="8" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.5">rules?</text>
        </g>

        <!-- Step 12: Side-by-side comparison -->
        <g id="comparison" opacity="0">
          <!-- Left side: blue AI blob (no structure) -->
          <text x="200" y="50" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="15" font-weight="600" fill="#2563eb">THE PITCH</text>
          <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="70" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.12" />
          <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="50" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.2" />
          <circle cx="200" cy="200" r="28" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.35" />
          <text x="200" y="205" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="16" font-weight="700" fill="#fff">AI</text>
          <!-- Chaos arrows -->
          <line x1="130" y1="140" x2="172" y2="176" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="130" y1="260" x2="175" y2="228" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="270" y1="140" x2="228" y2="176" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <line x1="270" y1="260" x2="225" y2="228" stroke="#2563eb" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3" />
          <!-- Generic AI model labels -->
          <text x="200" y="293" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#6b6b6b">any model...</text>
          <text x="200" y="315" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">interchangeable</text>
          <text x="200" y="335" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">execution engines</text>
          <!-- Contrast labels -->
          <text x="200" y="370" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">no audit trail</text>
          <text x="200" y="387" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">no accountability</text>
          <text x="200" y="404" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">black box</text>
          <text x="200" y="421" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">AI is everything</text>

          <!-- Divider -->
          <line x1="400" y1="70" x2="400" y2="460" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4 4" />

          <!-- Right side: authored system miniature (1.5x scale) -->
          <text x="600" y="50" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="15" font-weight="600" fill="#1a1a1a">THE SYSTEM</text>
          <!-- Mini primitives loop — scaled up -->
          <circle cx="510" cy="150" r="24" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <text x="510" y="154" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#1a1a1a">EVT</text>
          <rect x="571" y="126" width="48" height="48" rx="4" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <text x="595" y="154" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#1a1a1a">POL</text>
          <rect x="656" y="126" width="48" height="48" rx="4" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <text x="680" y="154" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#1a1a1a">PRC</text>
          <circle cx="680" cy="270" r="24" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <text x="680" y="274" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#1a1a1a">PER</text>
          <rect x="571" y="246" width="48" height="48" rx="8" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <text x="595" y="274" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#1a1a1a">AST</text>
          <rect x="486" y="246" width="48" height="48" rx="3" fill="#fafaf8" stroke="#1a1a1a" stroke-width="1.5" />
          <text x="510" y="274" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="9" fill="#1a1a1a">LGR</text>
          <!-- Mini connecting lines -->
          <line x1="534" y1="150" x2="571" y2="150" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <line x1="619" y1="150" x2="656" y2="150" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <line x1="680" y1="174" x2="680" y2="246" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <line x1="656" y1="270" x2="619" y2="270" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <line x1="571" y1="270" x2="534" y2="270" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="1.2" />
          <line x1="510" y1="246" x2="510" y2="174" stroke="#e5e5e3" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-dasharray="3 2" />
          <!-- AI at edges label -->
          <text x="600" y="320" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#2563eb">AI at the edges</text>
          <!-- Contrast labels -->
          <text x="600" y="348" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">proof in the ledger</text>
          <text x="600" y="365" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">named person</text>
          <text x="600" y="382" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">explicit rules</text>
          <text x="600" y="399" text-anchor="middle" font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#6b6b6b">AI is bounded + replaceable</text>
        </g>

        <!-- AI announce badge (pops center, flies to target) -->
        <g id="ai-announce" opacity="0" style="transform-origin: 400px 250px">
          <circle cx="400" cy="250" r="50" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.15" />
          <circle cx="400" cy="250" r="30" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0.3" />
          <text id="ai-announce-text" x="400" y="256" text-anchor="middle"
                font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="14"
                font-weight="700" fill="#2563eb"></text>
        </g>

        <!-- The dot (flows through the system) -->
        <circle id="dot" cx="150" cy="100" r="6" fill="#1a1a1a" opacity="0" />

        <!-- Clean dot that emerges from AI filter (step 8) -->
        <circle id="clean-dot" cx="150" cy="100" r="6" fill="#2563eb" opacity="0" />

      </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Scroll steps -->
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step" data-step="0">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>You run an operation.</h2>
          <p>Things happen. People respond. Assets get used. And someone has to answer for what happened and why.</p>
          <p>Property management. Field service. Healthcare. Logistics. Any business where the work is real, the people are accountable, and the outcomes matter.</p>
          <p>Your operation already has structure. Here's the framework for naming it.</p>
          <p class="step-label">Watch it come together. ↓</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="1">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>Something happened.</h2>
          <p>An event fires. But it just sits there. Nothing knows what to do with it.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> Homeowner reports a leak</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> Customer books a mow</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> Patient walks through the door</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="2">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>Now there's a rule.</h2>
          <p>A policy decides what happens next — who's eligible, what's allowed, what the constraints are.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> Water leak = emergency. 2-hour SLA. Notify owner.</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> Match crew by zone, rating, and availability</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> Triage: ESI Level 2. See within 10 minutes.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="3">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>Now there's a how.</h2>
          <p>Steps materialize. First this, then that. In order. With gates.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> Dispatch plumber. Confirm arrival. Document repair. Close.</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> Arrive. Assess. Mow. Edge. Blow. Photo. Complete.</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> Vitals. History. Assessment. Orders. Reassess.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="4">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>Now someone's accountable.</h2>
          <p>Not just anyone — someone qualified, available, and assigned by policy.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> Licensed plumber, within 15 miles, rated 4.5+</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> Crew lead certified for this property size</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> Attending physician, on shift, credentialed for trauma</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="5">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>Now there's a thing.</h2>
          <p>The asset — with identity, state, and history that persists across every event.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> Unit 4B kitchen — water heater, installed 2019, last inspected 7 months ago</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> 1247 Oak St — bermuda grass, 0.3 acres, last service 12 days ago</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> Bed 7 — patient, 58M, chest pain, prior cardiac history</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="6">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>Now there's proof.</h2>
          <p>The ledger records everything. Who did what, when, what they found. Append-only. Immutable.</p>
          <p>The record feeds back into future decisions.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> Plumber arrived 10:42am. Fixed supply line. Photos attached. Cost: $340.</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> Service complete 2:15pm. Before/after photos. Crew rating: 4.8.</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> Troponin negative. Discharged 14:30. Follow-up scheduled. Full chart documented.</div>
          </div>
          <p class="finale">Six primitives. Always six.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="7">
        <div class="step-content ai-step">
          <h2>But the real world is messy.</h2>
          <p>The event arrives as a photo. A voice note. A vague text. The system can't route a squiggle.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> "there's water coming from somewhere upstairs"</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> Blurry photo of overgrown yard, no address</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> "my chest feels weird" — no vitals, no history</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="8">
        <div class="step-content ai-step">
          <p class="ai-badge">AI MODE 1 — PERCEPTION</p>
          <h2>AI sees.</h2>
          <p>A thin blue layer between the mess and the system. The squiggle passes through — comes out structured. The system hums again.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> Photo → water damage, ceiling, severity: high, unit: 4B</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> GPS + photo → 1247 Oak St, overgrowth grade: heavy</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> Intake transcript → chest pain, 58M, onset 2hrs, no prior meds</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="9">
        <div class="step-content ai-step">
          <p class="ai-badge">AI MODE 2 — OPTIMIZATION</p>
          <h2>Three people can do the work.</h2>
          <p>Policy already filtered who's eligible. AI picks who's optimal — fastest, closest, least loaded. Policy decides who <em>can</em>. AI decides who <em>should</em>.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> 3 plumbers qualified → AI picks one: 4.8 rating, 3 miles, available now</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> 2 crews in zone → resequence routes, save 40 min</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> 4 attendings on shift → assign by current acuity load</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="10">
        <div class="step-content ai-step">
          <p class="ai-badge">AI MODE 3 — PATTERN DETECTION</p>
          <h2>AI reads the record.</h2>
          <p>The ledger has been filling up. AI scans it — finds what humans can't see. Recurring failures. Drifting SLAs. Procedures that stall at step 3. It proposes. Humans decide.</p>
          <div class="examples">
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Property</span> Unit 4B: 3rd water event in 14 months → recommend pipe replacement</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">Lawn Care</span> Crew B: 22% slower on similar lots → flag for review</div>
            <div class="example"><span class="example-label">ER</span> Door-to-doc trending up 12% over 6 weeks → staffing model alert</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="11">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>Structure first. Intelligence second.</h2>
          <p>The six primitives are the brain. AI is the senses — at the edges, never the center. Thin, bounded, replaceable.</p>
          <p class="finale">The brain is rules. The senses are AI. The record is proof.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="step" data-step="12">
        <div class="step-content">
          <h2>Two architectures.</h2>
          <p>One dumps everything into a blue box and hopes for the best. No audit trail. No accountability. No way to explain what happened or why.</p>
          <p>The other starts with structure — explicit rules, named people, proof in the ledger — then adds intelligence at the edges, where it belongs.</p>
          <p class="finale">One is a black box. The other is an authored system.</p>
          <div class="links">
            <a href="/">Principles</a>
            <a href="/essays">Essays</a>
            <a href="/glossary">Glossary</a>
            <a href="/architect">The Role</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
